'''Farnym''' were [[Sentience/Legends|sapient]] creatures noted for their roundness. They had close-cut orange fur and small noses. They had a peculiar odor that smelt of ginger mixed with sandalwood. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo's]] copilot aboard the [[Alderaan (yacht)|''Alderaan'']], [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Tchiery]], was a Farnym.

